{
  "texts": [
    "Sniffles2 is a complete redesign and extension of the SV caller Sniffles 28.",
    "Figure 1 gives an overview of its main components.",
    "Sniffles2 now implements repeat aware clustering to improve germline SV calling (Fig. 1a) and further enables family and population SV calling at scale and ease (Fig.",
    "1b) and implements methods to identify mosaic SVs (Fig. 1c).",
    "A detailed description of Sniffles2 can be found in the Methods section."
  ]
}